肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4f6a9c7491e95dee68e428f2da504b454c6a408","tid":1542363,"uid":2542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:24:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"422c7c69956e9c179f16019b3c2f28bee158879e","tid":1542363,"uid":31323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:32:41.000Z","msg":"五大訴求唔包解散狗隊<br />\n咁係咪又唔講得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山各自努力"},{"pid":"1e04b76bdceb6e447f594bdd84d202a2230552fa","tid":1542363,"uid":80630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:35:15.000Z","msg":"咁都唔叫割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1000000% 支持港獨但而家反對人出黎發起港獨<br />\n做乜撚？？？？？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就多得你地班人先唔成事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n口講唔割，但行動就割撚曬蓆<br />\n<br />\n由一開始我地淨係要撤回架咋，咁而家特首話撤回你係咪可以收工番屋企<br />\n咁你咪話唔係囉，因為仲有五大訴求丫嘛<br />\n<br />\n係囉，咁五大訴求係點黎？<br />\n就係其他問題逐漸浮現，發現撤回已經唔可以解決問題<br />\n所以先出現五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n而家經歷左咁多個月，咁多件事<br />\n我地發現五大訴求已經唔足夠，香港獨立先至係解決問題根本既方法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係啊你話好難，係好難，但<ins><strong>唔係唔得囉</strong></ins><br />\n明明個個都想獨立，但個個人都話唔得，咁點會成事呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想獨立唔係睇人地，係睇自己點諗<br />\n<br />\n如果你真係想獨立既話，就唔該唔好係到話因為人地唔支持，所以自己都唔支持<br />\n你理得人地要奶共話唔支持獨立姐，而家係你支唔支持獨立炸<br />\n痴撚線架咩？？？？<br />\n<br />\nD人夠話支持送中啦<br />\n咁你係咪話D人都支持送中，要求撤回係冇可能架<br />\n何況五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而家你想獨立，但你自己都唔支持，邊個黎支持？</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"fd0fb4364e7fcade063c27092710ce08046f381b","tid":1542363,"uid":6334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:53:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e8787111328d645a00f673a6f4f81876ec48851","tid":1542363,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:58:07.000Z","msg":"咪推依個on9 post"},{"pid":"e22ffbe4e1c11bb736a60a942e42c07b16929a3e","tid":1542363,"uid":2542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"422c7c69956e9c179f16019b3c2f28bee158879e","tid":1542363,"uid":31323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:32:41.000Z","msg":"五大訴求唔包解散狗隊<br />\n咁係咪又唔講得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山各自努力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:20:33.000Z","msg":"依個講得"},{"pid":"70f3e0cafe5938a18e6d4fcf108e922eb9adb888","tid":1542363,"uid":2542,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1e04b76bdceb6e447f594bdd84d202a2230552fa","tid":1542363,"uid":80630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:35:15.000Z","msg":"咁都唔叫割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1000000% 支持港獨但而家反對人出黎發起港獨<br />\n做乜撚？？？？？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br